etsysRtrAdvertNotificationMIB.name: etsysRtrAdvertNotificationMIB

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB module

etsysRtrAdvertNotificationMIB.contactinfo: Postal: Enterasys Networks 50 Minuteman Rd. Andover, MA 01810-1008 USA Phone: +1 978 684 1000 E-mail: support@enterasys.com WWW: http://www.enterasys.com
etsysRtrAdvertNotificationMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP MIB under the Enterasys Networks enterprise OID pertaining to router advertisement notifications. This MIB was designed to be used for monitoring router events that have occurred in the system related to router advertisements.

etsysRtrAdvertInconsistentEnabled.name: etsysRtrAdvertInconsistentEnabled
etsysRtrAdvertInconsistentEnabled.description: If this object is set to true (1) a trap will be sent when an inconsistent router advertisement is processed.

etsysRtrAdvertInetAddrType.name: etsysRtrAdvertInetAddrType
etsysRtrAdvertInetAddrType.description: A value that represents a type of Internet address specified by etsysRtrAdvertInetAddress.

etsysRtrAdvertInetAddress.name: etsysRtrAdvertInetAddress
etsysRtrAdvertInetAddress.description: The Internet Address of the router being advertised. The format of this object is defined by the etsysRtrAdvertInetAddrType object.

etsysRtrAdvertUserData.name: etsysRtrAdvertUserData
etsysRtrAdvertUserData.description: The data pertinent to the router advertisement notification being sent (i.e. mtu, hop-limit, etc.).

etsysRtrAdvertInconsistent.name: etsysRtrAdvertInconsistent
etsysRtrAdvertInconsistent.description: Inconsistent router advertisement notification. The device will send this notification when an inconsistent router advertisement is received from another router.

etsysRtrAdvertConfigGroup.name: etsysRtrAdvertConfigGroup
etsysRtrAdvertConfigGroup.description: A collection of objects providing basic instrumentation of router advertisement notifications.

etsysRtrAdvertInformationGroup.name: etsysRtrAdvertInformationGroup
etsysRtrAdvertInformationGroup.description: A collection of objects providing router advertisement information.

etsysRtrAdvertCompliance.name: etsysRtrAdvertCompliance
etsysRtrAdvertCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that support Enterasys router advertisement notifications.
